{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c76efcf5-9731-4509-8886-8cf533349d56","content":"The directory is empty — there's no project yet. No worries, here's exactly what you need to configure to publish a C# MCP server as a **dotnet tool** on NuGet.org:\n\n---\n\n### Key `.csproj` properties\n\nAdd these to your project file:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n\n  <!-- Makes this a dotnet tool -->\n  <PackAsTool>true</PackAsTool>\n  <ToolCommandName>my-mcp-server</ToolCommandName>\n\n  <!-- NuGet metadata -->\n  <PackageId>MyMcpServer</PackageId>\n  <Version>1.0.0</Version>\n  <Authors>YourName</Authors>\n  <Description>An MCP server for ...</Description>\n  <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>\n  <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>\n  <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/you/MyMcpServer</RepositoryUrl>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Steps to publish\n\n1. **Pack** the tool:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet pack -c Release\n   ```\n\n2. **Push** to NuGet.org (get an API key from [nuget.org/account/apikeys](https://www.nuget.org/account/apikeys)):\n   ```bash\n   dotnet nuget push bin/Release/MyMcpServer.1.0.0.nupkg \\\n     --api-key YOUR_API_KEY \\\n     --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n   ```\n\n3. **Users install** with:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet tool install -g MyMcpServer\n   my-mcp-server   # runs the stdio MCP server\n   ```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`PackAsTool`** is the critical property — it packages the exe as a global/local dotnet tool.\n- **`ToolCommandName`** controls the CLI command name users will type.\n- **`OutputType` must be `Exe`** (tools must be console apps).\n- For stdio MCP servers, no additional transport config is needed — the tool reads stdin/writes stdout naturally.\n\nWant me to scaffold the full project?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f6d9187b-ba0b-4b79-aac4-ded75896ed5b","outputTokens":576},"id":"eddc0040-ff1a-4ffa-bcf3-4f5850d42938","timestamp":"2026-04-04T00:43:32.281Z","parentId":"0273ebae-0db8-439f-9d0a-bcf53ebc69a4"}
